article.description: — Yaxel Lendeborg's 16 points and 15 rebounds helped UAB defeat Alabama A&M 93-82 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Yaxel Lendeborg has 16 points and 15 rebounds to lead UAB over Alabama A&M 93-82
article.linkText: Yaxel Lendeborg has 16 points and 15 rebounds to lead UAB over Alabama A&M 93-82
article.story: HUNTSVILLE, Ala. -- — Yaxel Lendeborg's 16 points and 15 rebounds helped UAB defeat Alabama A&M 93-82 on Wednesday night. Lendeborg also contributed four steals and three blocks for the Blazers (5-5). Eric Gaines scored 15 points and added seven assists. Efrem Johnson finished with 14 points. The Blazers shot 50% (30 of 60) overall and made 25 of 36 free throws. Dailin Smith led the way for the Bulldogs (1-9) with 27 points. Jayland Randall added 13 points for Alabama A&M. Omari Peek-Green also put up 12 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
